Congratulations @heisrema . You will do more Amen. All glory to GOD.  pic.twitter.com/acwy7mEgxr — ITS DON JAZZY AGAIN.  (@DONJAZZY) July 21, 2022 “Calm Down” is the fourth track off “Rave & Roses.” Rema released his much-anticipated debut album, “Rave & Roses”, back in March. Announcing the album’s release on Twitter, he wrote, “Here’s a piece of my soul to you, my debut Album Rave & roses out now. Thank you for the love & support over the years now, RAVE relentlessly! #RaveAndRoses “ Speaking to Apple Music about the album, he says, “I swear this album has different moods, different stories.” He notes that every project holds different meanings to him asides from the story they tell and says, “it’s that bridge to bring the fans closer to Rema.” Watch “Calm Down” by Rema: 